thread.title: BRIEF-Beijing Honggao Creative Architectural Design to swing to loss in FY 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Beijing Honggao Creative Architectural Design to swing to loss in FY 2017

organizations.name: beijing honggao creative architectural design co ltd

text:
Feb 1(Reuters) - Beijing Honggao Creative Architectural Design Co Ltd
* Sees to swing to net loss at 130 million yuan to 170 million yuan in FY 2017 versus net profit at 234.4 million yuan year ago
* Says increased provision of uncollectible accounts of accounts receivable is the main reason for the forecast
